measurements.description: Six flat stellate flowers and four buds on three up to 18-cm inflorescences; sepals and petals orange yellow, blushed red, red veins; lip yellow heavily overlaid magenta except throat, side lobes enclose column, throat veined magenta, keels yellow tinged red; substance firm; texture diamond dust.
